This paper discusses the ethical implications of machine learning systems, which is a common topic in the field of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also proposes a method for incorporating deontological constraints into machine learning models, which could fall under the category of cybersecurity (cs.CR) or social and information networks (cs.SI).
